!    Pomidor Plugin purpose:
!
!1. Highlight some keywords and special characters
!2. Display tomato icon - DONE
!
!    Pomidor syntax highlight rules:
!
!1. Markers @feature, @url and @data are color highlighted only at
!   the beginning of line
!2. Marker values (ex. smoke_test, login) are color highlighted one or more
!    space (space or tab) after marker
!3. Case-insensitive actions are highlighted. Actions are:
!    - click, clicks, clicked
!    - type, types, typed
!    - displayed, not_displayed (some more assert actions will be added later)
!4. '#' should get highlighted. (All page objects will be prefixed with '#'
!   by framework/plugin user)
!5. '[' and ']' are highlighted
!6. '<<' and '>>' are highlighted
!7. ' """ ' (triple double quotes) are highlighted


